<!-- Our Story -->
<section class="ibc-section" style="background:var(--ibc-gray-100)">
  <div class="ibc-container">
    <div class="ibc-about-content ibc-animate">
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>IBC Tank Store was founded in 2020 with a simple mission: to provide Pakistan's industries, farms, and
        businesses with reliable, high-quality IBC tanks at competitive prices. What started as a small warehouse in
        Lahore has grown into one of Pakistan's largest IBC tank distribution networks.</p>
      <p>We recognized a gap in the Pakistani market — businesses were struggling to find quality IBC tanks locally,
        often relying on expensive imports or settling for substandard alternatives. IBC Tank Store was created to solve
        this problem by providing a wide range of new and refurbished IBC tanks directly to customers across Pakistan.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>To be Pakistan's most trusted and reliable supplier of IBC tanks and storage solutions. We are committed to
        providing high-quality products, exceptional customer service, and competitive pricing to every customer —
        whether you're a small farm owner or a large industrial operation.</p>

      <h2>Why We're Different</h2>
      <p>Unlike generic sellers, we specialize exclusively in IBC tanks. This deep focus means we understand the unique
        storage needs of different industries — from agriculture and water storage to chemical handling and food
        processing. Our expert team helps you choose the right tank for your specific application.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

